// Wall plan: L-shaped wall for corner enclosure
// We'll use top-left corner by default
// Enclosure: rows 1..ER, cols 1..EC
// Walls: row ER+1 cols 1..EC, and col EC+1 rows 1..ER
// Plus corner at (ER+1, EC+1) to prevent diagonal leak
